<i>noun</i>: 손가락질 [손까락찔], 삿대질 [삳ː때질] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>손가락질 [손까락찔]</dt><br>
<dd>1. finger-pointing; pointing</dd><br>
<dd>손가락으로 무엇을 가리키는 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of indicating something with a finger.</dd><br>
<dd>2. criticism</dd><br>
<dd>남을 흉보는 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of finding fault with others.</dd><br>
<dt>삿대질 [삳ː때질]</dt><br>
<dd>finger-pointing; finger-wagging</dd><br>
<dd>상대를 향해 주먹이나 손가락을 힘차게 뻗음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of stretching out a finger or fist at the other party.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>